Nasty, nasty goddess. Zeboim is a bit jumpy. She could need someone to calm her down a bit I think. Blowing up storms is fun though, I would do that if I could. Not all the time like her though. That would get boring...
- Kender Child explaining Krynn mythology</p>
Zeboim dwells in Pandemonium, in the Layer of Phlegethon, in a Realm called Maelstrom.</p>
Relationships
Zeboim is the daughter of Takhisis and Sargonnas. Her brother is Nuitari. 
Sources: Dragonlance Adventures, Dragonlance Campaign Setting (Third Edition), On Hallowed Ground